{
  "text": "The test samples of micro nozzle/diffuser were then placed in a test rig to examine their performance. The present experimental setup to measure the total pressure drop across the nozzle/diffuser is the same as the one used in the study by Yang et al. [CITATION_1] . The total pressure drop \uf044P of micro nozzle/diffuser is often expressed in terms of the pressure loss coefficient \uf078, i.e.:",
